						               													<description>On &amp;quot;The Zombie Train&amp;quot;, human being have being infected by evil zombie virus vigorously...Based on the numerical comparison rules and abilities of different characters, you can either evacuate the survivors to a safe carriage, lead the zombies to invade the innocents,stop the evil virus spreading continuously. Now, it's time for you to save the innocent passengers on &amp;quot;The Zombie Train&amp;quot;!!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Goal of the game:&amp;#10;Difficulty of the requirements depends on the bonus points of each card. Based on the number of players, the player who scores the designated points first wins the game. &amp;#10;What do players do in their turns?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;step1&amp;#10;Based on the description on the back of the bonus card, among the three cards that the player is having, choose one card that represents how many human being the player wants to evacuate or zombies that he/she wants to lead to attack, then place it and pick one card from themask deck.(ex  there are many/not too much/a few  zombie/human in the car or bluffing the number of human/zombie&amp;#10;&amp;#10;step2&amp;#10;Train conductor will execute function first.Everyone take turns being train conductor&amp;#10;for every round.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;step3&amp;#10;Open the cards. If the total amount of human is more than zombies, then whoever has the biggest number wins; while the total amount of zombie is more than human, then who ever has the smallest number wins. The winner gets to choose a human card to evacuate to himself/herself&amp;rsquo;s carriage, or collect zombie and kill them. For those who wish to steal points from others, they can send zombies to other player&amp;rsquo;s carriages.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
